Subject: [PATCH 64/64] =?UTF-8?q?web-app:=20admin=20groups=20=E2=80=94=20c?=
 =?UTF-8?q?reate-dialog=20checkbox=20and=20admin-only=20management=20UI?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

UI for the core group-admins feature (ported from ArcaneChat's Android
client, ArcaneChat/android PR #167):

- New Group dialog: an "Admin group" checkbox creates the group via
  createGroupWithAdmin, making the creator the only one who can manage
  it.
- Group profile dialog: for non-admin members of an admin group, hide
  Add Member, QR invite code, member remove buttons and the Edit menu
  entry (core rejects those actions anyway).
- Chat menu: hide "Disappearing Messages" for non-admins of admin
  groups.
- Delete dialog: offer "Delete for Everyone" on other people's
  messages when you are the group admin.
